{"title":"hexo","uid":"45b05c0adc7d6b51711d3e13e977b9ba","slug":"hexo","date":"2024-01-28T08:31:17.000Z","updated":"2024-01-28T08:55:32.728Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>使用<a href=\"https://github.com/auroral-ui/hexo-theme-aurora\">hexo-theme-aurora</a>主题搭建自己的github博客网站。</p>\n<h1 id=\"引用图片\"><a href=\"#引用图片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引用图片\"></a>引用图片</h1><ol>\n<li><p>修改 <code>_config.yml</code></p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">post_asset_folder: true</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>保存图片</p>\n<p> 修改完配置后，<code>hexo new &lt;post&gt;</code> 后会在文章的同级目录生成一个和文章名相同的文件夹，将图片存入该文件夹</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">source</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">    _posts</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">        post1</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">        post1.md</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>插入图片</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">&#123;% asset_img [image] [title] %&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"智能机器人\"><a href=\"#智能机器人\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"智能机器人\"></a><a href=\"https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/en/configs/plugins.html#bot-dia\">智能机器人</a></h1><p>打开机器人，修改 <code>_config.aurora.yml</code>,</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">aurora_bot:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">  enable: true  # 打开</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">  locale: zh-CN  # 语言</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">  bot_type: dia</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">  tips:</span></span></code></pre></div>","feature":true,"text":"使用hexo-theme-aurora主题搭建自己的github博客网站。 引用图片 修改 _config.yml txtpost_asset_folder: ...","permalink":"/post/hexo","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":373,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/categories/hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"},{"name":"hexo-theme-aurora","slug":"hexo-theme-aurora","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hexo-theme-aurora.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">引用图片</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">智能机器人</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Rey","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/41515641?v=4","link":"/","description":"等风来还是追风去","socials":{"github":{"icon":"fat fa-github","link":"https://github.com/czp-first"},"twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"Apifox","uid":"09581b93998dfb7e17989c570be4419e","slug":"Apifox","date":"2024-01-28T07:54: